  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Enjoy your childhood again playing the all-time classic game of tag. Now updated to modern times with frogs slapping each other...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/ca85c13d022509c184917e74f685b2db.poster.avif?t=1741711011\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/ca85c13d022509c184917e74f685b2db.webm?t=1741711011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/ca85c13d022509c184917e74f685b2db.mp4?t=1741711011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All players must battle in a tenacious game of survival of the froggest, where one randomly selected player is possessed, and now is frog-hungry. Each player they manage to possess becomes one more weapon against the frogvivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/86929e6392663fae91403835bc54f3c3.avif?t=1741711011\" width=800 height=65 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online party game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Chat to express your hunger for frog.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short fast-paced matches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your frog to your liking choosing colors and skin patterns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Platformer mechanics to move nimbly around the maps.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/31104361b522c5283a6bcce5789d0866.avif?t=1741711011\" width=800 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of the match, a frog-player is randomly possessed. It only takes a few seconds to turn, so be careful as its structural frogginess becomes matched only by its hostility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/cbbe318a03f10e56a7bff85a7bff5912.avif?t=1741711011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras_big/cbbe318a03f10e56a7bff85a7bff5912.avif?t=1741711011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest of the frogs have to hide and escape. Be aware, the possessed frog is more powerful, and is unclouded by conscience or remorse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/d64451a316d4c19a31e5e3cb87ef21e5.avif?t=1741711011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras_big/d64451a316d4c19a31e5e3cb87ef21e5.avif?t=1741711011 width=800 height=450 /></span>When the possessed frog slaps another frog, it also becomes possessed.  So stay alert: as your friends are converted, your chances of survival grow thinner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/d975dc1aee05e0906e6ab55ff1fdeaed.avif?t=1741711011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras_big/d975dc1aee05e0906e6ab55ff1fdeaed.avif?t=1741711011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Enjoy your childhood again playing the all-time classic game of tag. Now updated to modern times with frogs slapping each other...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/ca85c13d022509c184917e74f685b2db.poster.avif?t=1741711011\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/ca85c13d022509c184917e74f685b2db.webm?t=1741711011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/ca85c13d022509c184917e74f685b2db.mp4?t=1741711011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All players must battle in a tenacious game of survival of the froggest, where one randomly selected player is possessed, and now is frog-hungry. Each player they manage to possess becomes one more weapon against the frogvivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/86929e6392663fae91403835bc54f3c3.avif?t=1741711011\" width=800 height=65 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online party game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Chat to express your hunger for frog.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short fast-paced matches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your frog to your liking choosing colors and skin patterns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Platformer mechanics to move nimbly around the maps.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/31104361b522c5283a6bcce5789d0866.avif?t=1741711011\" width=800 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of the match, a frog-player is randomly possessed. It only takes a few seconds to turn, so be careful as its structural frogginess becomes matched only by its hostility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/cbbe318a03f10e56a7bff85a7bff5912.avif?t=1741711011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras_big/cbbe318a03f10e56a7bff85a7bff5912.avif?t=1741711011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest of the frogs have to hide and escape. Be aware, the possessed frog is more powerful, and is unclouded by conscience or remorse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/d64451a316d4c19a31e5e3cb87ef21e5.avif?t=1741711011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras_big/d64451a316d4c19a31e5e3cb87ef21e5.avif?t=1741711011 width=800 height=450 /></span>When the possessed frog slaps another frog, it also becomes possessed.  So stay alert: as your friends are converted, your chances of survival grow thinner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras/d975dc1aee05e0906e6ab55ff1fdeaed.avif?t=1741711011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424870/extras_big/d975dc1aee05e0906e6ab55ff1fdeaed.avif?t=1741711011 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
